  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, there isn't specific information available about a character named **Prachi** in TVF's series titled **\"Humorously Yours.\"** It's possible that this character is part of a newer release or that the show has limited public information.\n\nTo find the real name of the actress portraying Prachi and to check if she is active on social media, I recommend the following steps:\n\n1. **Official Channels:**\n   - **TVF\u2019s Official Website:** Visit [TVF's official website](https://tvfplay.com/) to find detailed information about their latest shows and cast members.\n   - **Social Media:** Check TVF's official social media profiles on platforms like [Instagram](https://www.instagram.com/tvf/) and [Twitter](https://twitter.com/tvf_official) for announcements and updates.\n\n2. **Streaming Platform:**\n   - If \"Humorously Yours\" is available on a streaming platform like TVF Play or YouTube, the platform's description or credits section might list the cast and crew details.\n\n3. **Entertainment Databases:**\n   - Websites like [IMDb](https://www.imdb.com/) often have comprehensive cast lists and can be a valuable resource for finding information about specific characters and the actors who portray them.\n\n4. **Interviews and Press Releases:**\n   - Look for interviews, press releases, or promotional materials related to \"Humorously Yours.\" These often provide insights into the cast and their backgrounds.\n\nIf \"Humorously Yours\" is a very recent release or has limited exposure, information might still be forthcoming. Keeping an eye on the above sources will help you stay updated with the latest details about the character Prachi and the actress portraying her.",
